# Git Conventions

## Branches

```
feat/<ticket-id>-short-description
fix/<ticket-id>-short-description
chore/<description>
refactor/<description>
```

## Commit Format

`<type>(<scope>): <subject>` â€” max 72 chars, imperative mood

```
feat(auth): add refresh token rotation
fix(orders): handle null shipping address
refactor(payments): extract strategy pattern
chore(deps): upgrade typescript to 5.4
feat(api)!: remove deprecated v1 endpoints
```

Types: `feat` `fix` `refactor` `chore` `docs` `perf` `ci` `test`

- No period at end
- Breaking change: append `!` after type/scope
